node.title: Man dies in Auckland house fire
node.description: The fire occurred at 10:50pm on Friday night.
node.content: ["A man has died in a house fire in the Auckland suburb of Panmure on Friday night.\u00a0", "Police confirmed to Newshub the fire occurred at just after 10:50pm on Benghazi Road.\u00a0", "\"Sadly, a man has died in the fire. Police have a scene guard in place at the address, and fire investigators will be attending later today [Saturday],\" a police spokesperson told Newshub on Saturday.\u00a0\u00a0", "St John also confirmed to Newshub they received a call about the fire in Panmure and sent an ambulance in response to the incident.\u00a0", "Police said the incident has been referred to the Coroner.\u00a0"]
